name: Boney in Hallloween
description:
Bonehead is also known as Boney, He is a friendly soul who lives in his skull... His body size is very small almost like a tennis ball. He died by drowning when his parents left him in a box and threw him into the river. Boney was foolish, sloopy and childish but he has a pure hearts, always doing good and helping living things. He always had good fortune which made him believe that if one of his luck came from doing good things, he would get good in his life. Boney loves to draw, he always drew in any situation until the end of time.

I created Boney with alternate skin and ready for celebrating Halloween with his friends.
